import Layout from '../components/templates/defaults'
import { Hero } from '../components/organisms'
import {Container, Wrapper, View} from '../components/atoms'
import ImageHero from '../assets/illustrations/daily-resources.svg'

const App = () => {
    
    return (
        <>
            <Layout title="Daily Resources">
                <Hero 
                title="Daily Resources" 
                subtitle="The more that you read the more things you will know." 
                img={ImageHero}/>
                <Container isEqualWidth="100%" isEqualHeight="100vh">
                    <Wrapper>
                        <View className="half">
                            Content
                        </View>
                        <View className="half">
                            Content
                        </View>
                    </Wrapper>
                </Container>
            </Layout>
        </>
    )
}

export default App;
